<h2><b>High Fiver App: Testing Methodology</b></h2>

<p>
    I am comfortable writing unit tests and functional tests using PHPUnit.
    I would write basic unit tests for each operation of my objects, whether that is
    Doctrine ORM objects or objects used by the code base.
</p>
<p>
    I am comfortable configuring phpunit options, and setting up test suites for each part of
    the application and for the whole application.  I also am comfortable enabling xDebug to
    work in phpunit command line as well, so I can troubleshoot failing tests live.
</p>
